0 -16 Td
(## Findings & Patches Applied) Tj
0 -16 Td
() Tj
0 -16 Td
(### 1\) Client-side exposure of Gemini API key) Tj
0 -16 Td
(**Finding:** The build injected the Gemini key into the client bundle, which makes it retrievable by end users.) Tj
0 -16 Td
() Tj
0 -16 Td
(**Patch:** Added `VITE_ALLOW_CLIENT_AI_KEY` gate and disabled client key injection by default; `geminiService` only reads keys in development or when explicitly allowed. This reduces accidental key exposure in production.) Tj
0 -16 Td
() Tj
0 -16 Td
(**Files:**) Tj
0 -16 Td
(- `vite.config.ts`) Tj
0 -16 Td
(- `services/geminiService.ts`) Tj
0 -16 Td
() Tj
0 -16 Td
(### 2\) Token storage defaults to localStorage in production) Tj
0 -16 Td
(**Finding:** The auth service defaulted to `localStorage`, which increases XSS exposure in production.) Tj
0 -16 Td
() Tj
0 -16 Td
(**Patch:** Default token storage now uses secure cookies in production unless overridden by `VITE_TOKEN_STORAGE_MODE`. The session restoration path skips localStorage in cookie mode to avoid false logouts.) Tj
0 -16 Td
() Tj
0 -16 Td
(**Files:**) Tj
0 -16 Td
(- `services/authService.ts`) Tj
0 -16 Td
() Tj
0 -16 Td
(### 3\) Cookie-mode API requests did not include credentials) Tj
0 -16 Td
(**Finding:** When relying on httpOnly cookies, the API calls and AI proxy calls did not include `credentials: 'include'`, which would prevent cookies from being sent.) Tj
0 -16 Td
() Tj
0 -16 Td
(**Patch:** Added cookie-mode detection and ensured `credentials: 'include'` for API service calls, market data fetches, Gemini backend proxy, and sync device management calls.) Tj
0 -16 Td
() Tj
0 -16 Td
(**Files:**) Tj
0 -16 Td
(- `services/apiService.ts`) Tj
0 -16 Td
(- `hooks/useMarketData.ts`) Tj
0 -16 Td
(- `services/geminiService.ts`) Tj
0 -16 Td
(- `services/syncService.ts`) Tj
0 -16 Td
() Tj
0 -16 Td
(### 4\) Sync service uses an access token key that is never set) Tj
0 -16 Td
(**Finding:** Sync was reading `finpulse_access_token`, but auth only stores `finpulse_id_token`, causing sync authorization headers to be empty.) Tj
0 -16 Td
() Tj
0 -16 Td
(**Patch:** Added a token helper that reads `finpulse_id_token` first and falls back to `finpulse_access_token` for backward compatibility. This token is now used for sync fetch calls and reconnect logic.) Tj
0 -16 Td
() Tj
0 -16 Td
(**Files:**) Tj
0 -16 Td
(- `services/syncService.ts`) Tj
0 -16 Td
() Tj
0 -16 Td
(### 5\) Partial failures in market data fetch were hidden) Tj
0 -16 Td
(**Finding:** `Promise.allSettled` never threw, so API rejections were silently ignored and `error` was not updated.) Tj
0 -16 Td
() Tj
0 -16 Td
(**Patch:** Added rejection detection to surface a partial-error message while still displaying available data.) Tj
0 -16 Td
() Tj
